Objective
The goal of this assignment is to enhance the current chatbot to allow automatic method to appear on the page when the user comes to the page.

Assignment Overview
Append the chatbot that:

Chatbot pops up automatically when users appear on page
Same sequence follows
 

1. Backend Development
Use a programming language of your choice (e.g., PHP) & JavaScript.
Store questions and answers in a database (e.g., PostgreSQL) 
Implement logic to identify when the page has a user and appears to popup and generate chatbot
2. Frontend Development
Create a method that is hidden but the chatbot appears after it appears a user has been on the page for more than 10 seconds
3. Code Deployment
Submit code to GitHub
